(105, 'Why You Should Integrate A Payment Gateway', '2016-11-09', 'Web Development', '1478699982_Why-You-Should-Integrate-A-Payment-Gateway.png', '1478699982_Why-You-Should-Integrate-A-Payment-Gateway.png', 0, 'Integrate Payment gateway', 'Rebelute', 'Payment gateways are the most secure online link between customer and merchant for payments', 'Payment gateway, Web Design, Website development, E-commerce website design, ', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The Government of India in an overcome move have demonetized Rs.500 and Rs.1000 currency notes with a specific end goal to battle corruption and black money issue in the nation. The noteworthy move is required to contribute extraordinarily towards the country building. One of the divisions that will be to a great extent influenced is the e-commerce and retail industry in India.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Integration of payment gateway is a simple and easiest way to get out of such situation. A payment gateway permits your online store to acknowledge credit card payments from clients. A payment gateway is an application on an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/web-development-services&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;e-commerce website&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; that permits the site to interface the client payment account with the website&amp;rsquo;s account. Payment gateway takes into account the credit account detail elements to be secure rather being sent on the web. Web-based shopping has turned into a breeze with payment gateways. In basic terms, a payment gateway is what might as well be called a credit card processing facility that you would find in a physical store.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;This method of payment has &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;many advantages&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; over other methods, such as&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Guaranteed fraud protection Mechanisms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Customer personal data protection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Ease of access and use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Supports multi-currency payment processing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How does a payment gateway function? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;There are four basic strides in the payment gateway process:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p