(106, 'Virtual Reality in Real Estate', '2016-11-11', 'Real Estate Industry', '1478866931_Virtual-Reality-in-Real-Estate.png', '1478866931_Virtual-Reality-in-Real-Estate.png', 0, 'Virtual Reality in Real Estate', 'Rebelute', 'The future of technology in Real Estate is Virtual Reality', 'Real Estate Digital Marketing, Online promotion, Digital Networking Strategy for Real Estate, Digital marketing for Real Estate Industry', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The future of technology: Virtual reality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:calibri; font-size:13.3333px&quot;&gt;Virtual reality or virtual realities (VR), otherwise called immersive multimedia and computer-simulated reality, is a computer technology that repeats a situation, genuine or envisioned, and reenacts a client&amp;#39;s physical presence that environment in a way that permits the client to connect with it. It was initially considered as a digitally made space which people could access by wearing unique computer types of gadgets . It empowers individuals to manage data all the more effectively. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:calibri; font-size:13.3333px&quot;&gt;2016 resembles the most essential year: it will be the first time that consumers can be provided a different way to see and experience information, one that is dynamic and immediate. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is Virtual Reality?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:calibri; font-size:13.3333px&quot;&gt;Virtual Reality (VR) is the utilization of computer innovation to make a mimicked surrounding. Not at all like conventional UIs, VR places the client inside an experience. Rather than survey a screen before them, clients are drenched and ready to connect with 3D universes. By mimicking however many faculties as could reasonably be expected, for example, vision, hearing, touch, even notice, the PC is changed into a guardian to this artificial world. Virtual reality can be characterized as an up and coming innovation that makes clients feel in a Virtual Environment (VE) by utilizing computer equipment and programming.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Virtual Reality technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:calibri; font-size:13.3333px&quot;&gt;Virtual reality technology confronts various difficulties, a large portion of which include movement ailment and specialized matters. Virtual Reality&amp;#39;s most quickly conspicuous segment is the head-mounted display (HMD). People are visual animals, and display technology is frequently the single greatest contrast between immersive Virtual Reality frameworks and conventional User interfaces. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:calibri; font-size:13.3333px&quot;&gt;In Virtual Reality, the PC utilizes comparable sensors and math. In any case, instead of finding a genuine camera inside a physical situation, the position of the client&amp;#39;s eyes are situated inside the reproduced environment. On the off chance that the client&amp;#39;s head turns, the illustrations respond as needs be. As opposed to compositing virtual articles and a genuine scene, VR technology makes a convincing, intuitive world for the client.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Major players in Virtual Reality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:calibri; font-size:13.3333px&quot;&gt;Oculus Rift, Oculus VR and Facebook, Google Cardboard, Samsung GearVR and Epson Movario are leading the way but there are also players like Meta, Avegant Glyph, Daqri and Magic Leap who may surprise the industry with new levels of immersion and usability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How Virtual Reality is being used today&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-fami