(55, '20', 'Google is taking Accelerated Mobile Pages (AMP) beyond the fold', '0', 'google-is-taking-accelerated-mobile-pages-beyond-the-fold', 'Google Expands AMP in Search Results for Faster Mobile Web', '2016-08-04', '1470315802Google-anouncement-AMP-Rebelute.png', '', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Google declared that they&amp;#39;ve added another channel to the Search Analytics report inside Google Search Console to channel reports by AMP pages. Presently Google is taking &lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot;&gt;Accelerated Mobile Pages (AMP)&lt;/a&gt; past the &amp;quot;Top Stories&amp;quot; and into the principle natural versatile query items. Growing connections to Accelerated Mobile Pages past a merry go round at the highest point of its list items to the full once-over of results. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;This means&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;mobile search clients will soon begin to content in indexed lists with the AMP lightning jolt logo, showing the substance is accessible in the portable configuration &amp;mdash; practically identical to &amp;quot;mobile friendly.&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;Google has been showing AMP pages in a merry go round expected to highlight news articles, where the activity started. In the meantime, the mobile mammoth has been urging advanced retailers to begin utilizing the AMP design for the versatile locales, enlisting about six to take an interest.&lt;/span&g