(56, '20', 'Are you keeping up with Facebook’s latest features?', '0', 'are-you-keeping-up-with-facebook-latest-features', 'Facebook declared two new Page areas - Services and Shop - for developing markets', '2016-08-05', '1470399946Facebook_features-Rebelute.png', '', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Are you staying &lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot;&gt;Aware of Social media&amp;#39;s&lt;/a&gt; most recent updates? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;A portion of the recent Facebook components could largely affect your business as universally more than one billion individuals on Facebook are associated. In a move to make its Pages highlight significant for organizations on the web, Facebook declared two new Page areas - Services and Shop - for developing markets incorporating into India too.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;The Shop area gives organizations another approach to unmistakably show the items they are offering on their Page. It permits individuals to effectively find, peruse and make offers to buy items through informing from the organizations they think about, Facebook said in an announcement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;The Services area permits service businesses to showcase a rundown of their offerings on their Page. Utilize these new components to build your business&amp;#39; perceivability and better associate with your clients, and also to start thoughts of how you can enhance your business stream and you&amp;#39;re showcasing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;With the Shops and Services segments on Pages, organizations around the globe can individuals find the products and services they think about in an all the more outwardly engaging way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '2016-08-05 12:25:46'),
(57, '20', 'Twitter launched hundreds of new emoji for Rio 2016', '0', 'twitter-launched-hundreds-of-new-emoji-for-rio-2016', 'Twitter, which is the first social platform included new emojis for the Rio Olympic Game Fans', '2016-08-08', '1470651328TWitter Emoji News.png', '', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family:arial; font-size:14px&quot;&gt;The &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2016 Summer Olympics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family:arial; font-size:14px&quot;&gt; officially known as the Games of the XXXI Olympiad and commonly known as &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rio 2016&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family:arial; font-size:14px&quot;&gt;, is a major international multi-sport event in the tradition of the Olympic Games as governed by the International Olympic Committee, being held in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The Rio 2016 Olympic Games begin on Saturday with the opening ceremony at Maracana Stadium.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Twitter, which is the first &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;social media platform&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; included new emojis for the Rio Olympic Game Fans. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Fans across the globe can now share their passion for their favourite teams with 207 hashtag-triggered team emojis. Tweeting with the three-letter country code hashtag &amp;mdash; #IND for India &amp;mdash; will trigger flag emojis for every team, including the Refugee Olympic Team (#ROT).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;You will also be able to trigger over 50 Olympics and sports emojis, which are available in English, French, Portuguese and Spanish. Most of these (208) are team flags that can be activated using hashtags with three-letter country codes (e.g. #USA), but 54 of them are for either sports or Olympics-related symbols. The hashtags that trigger sports emojis, as well as #Rio2016 and #Olympics, are also available in Japanese, Korean and Arabic.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '2016-08-08 10:15:28'),
(58, '20', 'Facebook Pages have encountered a 52% decrease in organic reach this year', '0', 'facebook-pages-have-encountered-a-52-percent-decrease-in-organic-reach-this-year', 'Facebook Pages have encountered a 52% decrease in organic reach this year', '2016-08-09', '1470742835Facbook_Fall_Rebelute.png', '', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;A well known&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt; Search Engine Optimization agency&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; investigated the Facebook pages of approximately 3,000 media organizations that utilization its platform from January through May, and it found that scope per post for those pages plunged 42 percent. Facebook Pages have encountered a 52-percent decrease in organic reach that is 10 percent &amp;nbsp;more than the previous report. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;Facebook declared that it would make Pages&amp;#39; organic reach more subject to individuals sharing their posts than a Page post specifically showing up in somebody&amp;#39;s feed. It&amp;#39;s misty the amount of effect the calculation change would have had on SocialFlow&amp;#39;s information; the Facebook representative said the general effect for Pages ought to be little. Additionally clear is the means by which distributors can adjust to, if not stay away from, the decrease in natural span.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;With regards to the content they post to Facebook, video gives off an impression of being something of a lifesaver.Facebook has made its news sustain calculation more aware of video, added general visibility checks to make individuals more aware of how well known video is on Facebook, and its executives have even anticipated that Facebook &amp;quot;will be presumably all video&amp;quot; in five years.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-08-09 11:40:35'),
(59, '20', 'Google Maps added two new Offline Features', '0', 'google-maps-added-two-new-offline-features', ' Google Maps has added more international ride-service options to compare rates in a number of countries.', '2016-08-10', '1470815334Google-Maps-Update-Rebelute.png', '', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Driving around your own particular city can be a fight and exploring around a foreign area can be ten times harder. Utilizing Google Maps offline and looking at between service administration alternatives make it somewhat less demanding so you can invest more energy living and less time making sense of how to get places. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;Notwithstanding the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maps.googleblog.com/2016/08/get-around-town-little-easier-with-new.html?m=1&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;two new offline features&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;, Google Maps has likewise increased the quantity of universal ride-service postings to think about rates in various nations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;Agreeing the declaration, Android clients with spotty administration &amp;ndash; or clients who might need to save money on information &amp;ndash; can turn on the new &amp;quot;Wi-fi Only&amp;quot; element in their Google Maps settings to utilize the application when they&amp;#39;re disconnected.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;Google Maps likewise added the capacity to spare a region to an outer SD card on Android gadgets so that any spared maps don&amp;#39;t need to take up interior storage room. Android clients will be offered the choice to spare the a guide to their telephone or SD Card when they select to download a range.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '2016-08-10 07:48:54'),
(60, '20', 'Google has confirmed the rollout of the new user interface to AdWords users', '0', 'google-has-confirmed-the-rollout-of-the-new-user-interface-to-adwords-users', 'The change help advertisers reach across the spectrum of  search, display, shopping, mobile and video.', '2016-08-11', '1470913338GoogleAdwordsUpdate.png', '', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Google has confirmed the rollout of the new user interface to more AdWords users.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;The days of predictable web sessions have been replaced by numerous short bursts of digital activity throughout the day, primarily on mobile.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The innovations in AdWords that make these experiences possible have helped many businesses reach their customers in better, smarter ways. &amp;nbsp;In regard to the new interface surfacing, a Google Representative has confirmed that the interface is rolling out to more users. It should be noted that this move is purely an interface design change &amp;mdash; it will not change the core functionality of AdWords. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Paul Feng, AdWords product management director, had stated that the change will help advertisers reach across the spectrum of &amp;nbsp;search, display, shopping, mobile and video. In Addition, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://adwords.googleblog.com/2016/03/redesigning-adwords-for-the-mobile-first-marketer.html&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Google has stated:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Through 2016 and into 2017, we&amp;rsquo;ll continue to build out this new AdWords experience, and invite advertisers along the way to try it out and provide feedback. Invites will be sent based on a number of factors, therefore not all advertisers will be able to test the new experience right away.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '2016-08-11 11:02:18');
