(61, '20', 'Make your Email Better at The Email Design Conference, Boston', '0', 'make-your-email-better-at-the-email-design-conference-boston', 'Email marketing is about making a relationship with your customer', '2016-08-12', '1470993797Email-Design-Conference-Rebelute.png', 'Make Your Email Better', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;How would we need individuals to feel when they open an email? For most advertisers, the answer is propelled, energized, inquisitive, persuaded. These feelings help individuals to do activities such as purchasing, connecting with, or upholding for a brand inside their own particular systems. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/category-blogs/Email-Marketing&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Email marketing&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;is about making a relationship with your customer. That infers your messages ought to be appropriate and favorable for each customer, and not each one of your customers are the same.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Email is the spine all through a customer&amp;#39;s experience as it&amp;#39;s basic to look at it past terms, for instance, open rate and snap through,&amp;quot; reports says. &amp;quot;Those estimations aren&amp;#39;t as is normally done wrong, yet they measure the transient effect of a single correspondence. What we&amp;#39;re got notice from associations is that they need the ability to gage email&amp;#39;s whole deal effect of how customers are seeing their brands.&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Email Design Conference&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; (https://litmus.com/conference/boston) unites the email group to praise their specialty and give advertisers and architects a stage to learn, share, and develop. so don&amp;#39;t wait for the moment. Right time is now only. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-08-12 09:23:17'),
(62, '20', 'E-commerce sales grew 15.8% in the second quarter.', '0', 'e-commerce-sales-grew-16-percent-in-the-second-quarter', 'Online retail came in at $97.3 billion in the second quarter of the year, as indicated by the Commerce Department', '2016-08-17', '1471428302ECommerce.png', 'E Commerce Rebelute Digital Solutions', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The Department of Commerce declared that &lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot;&gt;e-commerce sales&lt;/a&gt; for the second quarter were $97.3 billion, out of $1.2 trillion in absolute US retail sales. Considering out the offers of items not regularly led on the web, e-business represented 10.9% of retail deals amid the period. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The Commerce Department reported online retail deals came to $91.24 billion, a 15.8% expansion contrasted and the same time a year ago. This is the biggest year-over-year development rate subsequent to the second from last quarter of 2014, when e-commerce deals grew 16.2% contrasted and the year earlier.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;In examination, add up to retail sales barring food service came to $1.22 trillion amid the three months finished June 30, a 2.1% expansion. That implies e-business represented around 7.5% of aggregate retail deals barring sustenance administration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Source: https://www.internetretailer.com/2016/08/16/us-e-commerce-posts-its-largest-gain-nearly-two-years&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '2016-08-17 10:05:02'),
