(65, '20', 'Index Status Report Is found Broken in Google Search Console', '0', 'index-status-report-is-found-broken-in-google-search-console', 'Index Status Report Is found Broken in Google Search Console. Google added that there is no estimated time for this report to be fixed', '2016-08-23', '1471958379Google-Search-Console-Rebelute.png', 'Google Index Status Report Rebelute Digital Solutions', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Gary Illyes from Google has confirmed on Twitter that the index status report within the Google Search console is &amp;quot;broken right now.&amp;quot; So Google is aware of the issues but the index status count may not be accurate for you. Also added that there is no estimated time for this report to be fixed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Some are noticing that the report, which shows webmasters how many pages &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com&quot;&gt;Google&lt;/a&gt; has indexed of the site, has not grown in number, as they would expect. Some compared the index status report flat growth to that of the Sitemap report index count. And when the numbers don&amp;rsquo;t align and shift together, it may be a sign that one of the reports is wrong. So for now, rely on your Sitemap index report in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/&quot;&gt;Google Search Console.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '2016-08-23 13:19:39'),
(66, '20', 'WhatsApp start offering your phone data to Facebook', '0', 'whatsapp-start-offering-your-phone-data-to-facebook', 'WhatsApp start offering more information to Facebook and will begin giving a few organizations a chance to send messages to clients', '2016-08-26', '1472204786whatsapp_Facbook_rebelute.png', 'WhatsApp-Facebook-Rebelute', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;WhatsApp will start to arrange accounts with Facebook by sharing WhatsApp clients&amp;#39; cellular telephone numbers and device data like the kind of operating system and different insights about the cell phone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;The progressions to the terms and conditions permit &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/rebelutedigital&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Facebook&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt; to see the telephone number that individuals use with their WhatsApp account. That gives them a method for following individuals that is shared over the two destinations, helping Facebook assemble information for advertisements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;This implies if a man has the applications of Facebook and WhatsApp introduced on the same device, even with various telephone numbers, Facebook will now be able to map the two in the background using the basic device information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&