(69, '21', 'All you want to know about iPhone 7 and iPhone 7 Plus', '0', 'all-you-want-to-know-about-iphone-7-and-iphone-7-plus', 'Apple\\''s iPhone 7 and 7 Plus are newest iPhones with latest features. ', '2016-09-09', '1473492628iphone-7.png', 'Latest iPhone 7 Features ', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;At a pressed Bill Graham Civic Auditorium in San Francisco Sept. 7, Apple declared its most recent exhibit smart phones &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;iPhone 7&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;iPhone 7 Plus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;, including two new iPhones, an upgraded &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Apple Watch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;, and another arrangement of remote earphones called &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AirPods&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;AirPods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;Apple reported that, in evacuating the 3.5mm jack, the included earphones will work over Apple&amp;#39;s Lightning standard. Apple built up its own particular standard to permit remote earphones to interface with the new iPhones consistently. Utilizing its own particular W1 chip, Apple outlined AirPods &amp;mdash; or EarPods without wires &amp;mdash; that associate with the iPhone without expecting to combine like you would with Bluetooth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px; line-height:1.6em&quot;&gt;Camera&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); fon