(73, '21', 'Which is the most important movement in the process of business growth? ', '0', 'which-is-the-most-important-movement-in-the-process-of-business-growth', 'Which is the most important movement in the process of business growth? ', '2016-09-30', '1475242890Gitex-tech-2016.png', 'Gitex Technology Week 2016', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Which is the most important movement in the process of business growth? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The answer is obvious! NETWORKING. At GITEX you will get the chance to create a vital network with the industry experts, professionals, technology geeks,influencers &amp;amp; senior decision makers. Where you can explore yourself. Businesses of all shapes and sizes are upgrading their systems, investing in technical expertise and becoming a technology led organizations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;GITEX is a platform having an access to investments, business and various chances to work in partnership with the most influential industry leaders from all around the world with the technology community.You will get a chance to learn a lot about the strategies, technology innovations, latest trends in the industry, various case studies from the experienced professionals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Understanding the scope of business growth, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Rebelute Digital Solutions&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;sp