(76, '22', 'What’s in Android 7.1?', '0', 'what-is-in-android-7-1', 'Android 7.1 delivers the productivity, security, and performance of Android 7.0', '2016-10-12', '1476266915Android 7.1.png', 'Android 7.1', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Google has &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://android-developers.blogspot.in/2016/10/android-71-developer-preview.html&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;declared&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Android 7.1 Nougat developer preview&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; will be released before October end. It&amp;#39;s an incremental redesign in view of Android 7.0, yet incorporates new elements for purchasers and developers &amp;mdash; from &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;platform Daydream VR support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; A/B framework updates&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;app shortcuts&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; images keyboard support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;. Android 7.1 conveys the profitability, security, and execution of Android 7.0, alongside an assortment of improvements and bug fixes, highlights, and new APIs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;For designers, Android 7.1 adds new capacities to drive engagement in application and convey &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/mobile-development&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;an enhanced user experience&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;, for example, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Application shortcuts API&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; &amp;mdash; surface important activities for their applications straightforwardly in the launcher, immediately taking their clients deep into their application. Applications can have 5 shortcuts, either statically or progressively. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Circular application symbols support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; &amp;mdash; give awesome looking adjusted symbol assets that match the look of Pixel and different launchers. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Worked in upgraded live wallpaper metadata&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; &amp;mdash; as a Storage Manager aim which lets an application take the client straight to another Settings screen to clear unused documents and free up storage room. Can demonstrate existing metadata, for example, label, description, and author, and additionally another connection URL and title to link to more data. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Image Keyboard bolster&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; &amp;mdash; extends the sorts of substance that clients can enter from their keyboards, letting them communicate through custom stickers, energized gifs, and many more. Applications can tell the keyboard what sorts of substance they acknowledge, and keyboards can convey the greater part of the pictures and other substance that they offer to the client. For wide similarity, this API will likewise be accessible in the support library. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;For bearers and calling applications there will be new APIs supporting multi-endpoint calling and new communication design choices.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-10-12 10:08:35'),
(77, '22', 'Be a part of the next level technology and innovation event GITEX 2016 ', '0', 'be-a-part-of-the-next-level-technology-and-innovation-event-gitex-2016', 'Meet with Team Rebelute to understand the business panorama at GITEX Technology Week DUBAI 2016', '2016-10-14', '1476445419Gitex_New.png', 'Gitex Technology Week 2016 Rebelute', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;GITEX (&amp;quot;Gulf Information Technology Exhibition&amp;quot;) is a yearly customer computer and electronics trade show, presentation, and gathering that happens in &lt;strong&gt;Dubai, United Arab Emirates&lt;/strong&gt; at the&lt;strong&gt; Dubai World Trade Center&lt;/strong&gt;. This event in the Middle East have pulled in various participants, for example, startups, investors, entrepreneurs, tech leaders, founders &amp;amp; mentors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Technologies, for example, cloud, mobile, social, digital and big data analytics have turned into a center a portion of cutting edge IT and establish the framework of digital transformation. &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GITEX Technology week&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; is the ideal place to locate these most recent technologies. Aptitudes for new and developing technology is dependably a test, and vendors should search out accomplices that are prepared to support investment in allotting headcount for the innovative solutions. This is an entrance to ventures, business and an opportunity to work in organization with the most compelling industry pioneers from the innovation group.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;GITEX Technology Week is one of the biggest occasions, and it is a passage for worldwide brands to get to the quickest developing venture prepared Information and Communications Technology advertise. Understanding this scope, &lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com&quot;&gt;Rebelute Digital Solutions&lt;/a&gt; has decided to participate in &lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/gitex-2016&quot;&gt;GITEX Technology Week&lt;/a&gt;. Looking forward to meet with you at GITEX 2016, Dubai.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-10-14 11:43:39'),
(78, '22', 'Google’s Video Sharing Website YouTube Has Acquired Famebit', '0', 'googles-video-sharing-website-youtube-has-acquired-famebit', 'Youtube has acquired FameBit, a marketplace where video makers can connect with brands interested in sponsoring their creations', '2016-10-17', '1476688406Famebit.png', 'Youtube acquire Famebit', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Google claimed YouTube on Tuesday 11th Oct 2016 reported it has purchased FameBit, a commercial center where video creators can associate with brands intrigued by supporting their manifestations. However, did not unveil money related terms of the deal, which it depicted as a technology platform that helps makers and brands make matches prompting sponsorships or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;paid promotions&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Nine years back, YouTube propelled its Partner Program with the objective of helping makers procure promoting income while associating their inventive contents to gatherings of people worldwide. Consistently, more brands are making YouTube vital to their advertising strategy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;As brands keep on embracing the estimation of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-MH2owuZqGy5nL-G2mF5NA&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;YouTube&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;, they&amp;#39;re likewise making their ventures one step further, collaborating with makers on branded content opportunities such as product placements, promotions and sponsorships.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Now looking to the future, Google has gained FameBit to create more creators and brands to come together and realize the benefits of these creative collaborations . This collaboration will expand the quantity of marked content openings accessible, bringing much more income into the online video group. FameBit&amp;#39;s democratized commercial center will permit makers of all sizes to specifically associate with brands, and also give an awesome innovation answer for organizations like MCNs and offices to discover matches for their makers and brand accomplices. The ultimate goal is to convey more income to the group of online video makers that are integral to YouTube.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-10-17 07:13:26'),
(79, '22', 'The Function \\"Demote Sitelinks\\" in Search Console is No More', '0', 'the-function-demote-sitelinks-in-search-console-is-no-more', 'Google Search console has removed the function Demote Sitelinks will affect the digital marketing community', '2016-10-20', '1476947277Google_search_Console.png', 'Google Search Console', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Google shows some of the links from your site when somebody searches for your brand name or site name in Google.Such links are called sitelinks. Google has their algorithm to decide such links, but pages that are very much connected and most well known on your blog are shown as sitelink.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Of course when Google shows sitelink, we have almost no power over it however we generally have the consent to piece sitelinks which we would prefer not to appear in output.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;On 13th Oct 2016, Google&amp;rsquo;s Webmasters Community has declared that this feature is going to be removed to simplify things. Google included:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Our algorithms have become much better at discovering, making and indicating significant sitelinks, thus we feel it&amp;#39;s a great opportunity to streamline things. We just show sitelinks for results when we think they&amp;#39;ll be valuable to the client. In the event that the structure of your site doesn&amp;#39;t permit our algorithms to discover great sitelinks, or we don&amp;#39;t surmise that the sitelinks for your site are significant for the client&amp;#39;s query, we won&amp;#39;t show them. This procedure is totally automated. Sitelinks have developed into being founded on conventional web ranking, so the best approach to impact them is the same as other site pages.&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Google listed three best practices if we don&amp;rsquo;t want to show up any sitelink: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Provide a clear structure for your website, using relevant internal links and anchor text that&amp;rsquo;s informative, compact and avoids repetition.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Allow Google to crawl and index important pages within your site. Use Fetch and Render to check that they can be rendered properly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;If you need to remove a page from search completely, use a &amp;ldquo;noindex&amp;rdquo; robots meta tag on that page.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Sitelinks can be a great way to make more conversions as they lead customers directly to the products and services page they need most.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-10-20 07:07:57'),
(80, '22', 'Exclusive updates from GITEX Technology Week 2016', '0', 'exclusive-updates-from-gitex-technology-week-2016', 'GITEX Technology Week 2016 was a gathering of all the new ideas and information of Latest Technologies. ', '2016-10-24', '1477304068Gitex_Update.png', 'Updates from GITEX 2016', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;GITEX Technology Week started on 16th Oct 2016 with a bouquet of multinational technology companies showing their latest products and services. GITEX 2016 was like a gathering of all the new ideas and information on robotics, 3D printing, virtual reality, augmented reality, drones, startups and live demos of latest technologies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Technology giants like IBM &amp;amp; Microsoft, E-commerce companies like Alibaba has perfectly shown how &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Digital transformation&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; is grabbing the central stage. There was few more technologies which were successful in making their place between the future technology platform like &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Virtual reality, Augmented Reality, Cloud Computing, Artificial Intelligence, Digital Marketing, Big Data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; and many more. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Team &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Rebelute&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; at the event also observe a converged and hyper-converged infrastructure, adoption of cloud, Big Data and IoT as the main technologies that are going to drive future growth of any business. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The five-day event witnessed the most global weeklong start-up event in 2016, more than 410 startups from 60 countries and 1,200 tech founders is an achievement. The Gitex Technology Week theme of &amp;lsquo;Re-Imagining Realities&amp;rsquo; emphasizes the practical steps that organizations need to take in their digital transformation, and the potential for enabling the life-changing ideas for entrepreneurs. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-10-24 10:14:28'),
(81, '22', 'Why Mobile Apps Are Profitable For Your Business?', '0', 'why-mobile-apps-are-profitable-for-your-business', 'Having a Mobile App for your business becomes necessary as it spread to every sector. ', '2016-10-26', '1477462165Mobile apps For Your Business.png', 'Mobile App for Business', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Having a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/mobile-development&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Mobile App for your business&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; becomes necessary in this Tech-world. Mobile applications have spread to almost all the sectors: Business, Catalogues, Finance, Food &amp;amp; Beverages, Entertainment, Health, Finances, E-commerce, Sports, Navigation, LifeStyle, Enterprise, Social Network, Productivity, Utilities, Travel, and many more. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;A report shows that the global mobile app market is projected to reach $51 billion in 2016 across all app stores. By 2020, gross revenue across all app stores will exceed $101 billion globally. And total mobile app downloads is forecast to exceed 210 billion, generating nearly $57 billion in revenue by 2020.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Now, the industry has started talking about a post-app era, with technologies like,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Internet of Things(IoT), artificial intelligence(AI), virtual reality(VR) and augmented reality(AR)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;gaining traction. With AR-based apps, users can feel a magical realism around their physical world. This becomes possible with the help of a smartphone&amp;rsquo;s GPS system and other digital, sensory and graphic technologies.This technology opens a sea of opportunities for the IT industry. &amp;nbsp;It grabbed the attention recently with the launch of AR-based Pokemon Go game, which made the world go crazy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;It is recommended that the organizations should prepare themselves by being agile and tactical, planning for new skills, assessing the new opportunities created by the post-app era, and developing a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;digital business strategy&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; that integrates many different technologies. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '2016-10-26 06:09:25'),
(82, '23', 'Digital Advertising Income Have Achieved An Untouched Height in 2016', '0', 'digital-advertising-income-have-achieved-an-untouched-height-in-2016', 'The digital advertising industry has shown its achievement in the year 2016.', '2016-11-04', '1478263622Digital_Advertising.png', 'Digital Advertising Market ', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;As indicated by the most recent&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; IAB&amp;rsquo;s Internet Advertising Revenue Report&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;discharged by the business exchange group, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;digital advertising&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; incomes in the United States for the principal half of 2016 have achieved an untouched high, scaling to $32.7 billion. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Comprehensive, the report incorporates information reflecting online advertising revenues from Web sites, commercial online services, Email providers, and additionally different organizations offering web-based promoting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Different highlights from the 2016 Half-Year Report include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Mobile income saw the biggest year-over-year change, moving to $15.5 billion, up 89% from $8.2 billion in HY 2015. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Taking a more profound jump into mobile, video on cell phones and tablets saw solid triple-digit development, achieving $1.6 billion in HY 2016, a great 178% ascent from HY 2015. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Mobile Search took a critical uptick, acknowledging $7.4 billion in HY 2016, a 105% expansion contrasted with $3.6 billion in HY 2015. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Add up to digital video, including mobile and desktop, rose to $3.9 billion in HY 2016, up 51% from $2.6 billion in HY 2015. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Search ads, including mobile and desktop, represents half of all digital advertising income, and hit $16.3 billion in HY 2016, a 19% climb over the $13.7 billion produced in HY 2015. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Add up to online networking incomes, including versatile and desktop, surged to $7 billion in HY 2016, a 57% ascent contrasted with $4.4 billion in HY 2015.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Of the segment verticals measured, the main three keep on amassing about a portion of all advertisement burn through (46%)&amp;mdash; retail (21%), budgetary administrations (13%), and car (12%).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', '2016-11-04 12:47:02'),
(83, '23', 'Google Is Moving Towards A More Mobile Focused Index', '0', 'google-is-moving-towards-a-more-mobile-focused-index', 'Google has started testing its mobile first index, which will basically take a gander at the mobile form of your site for its ranking signs', '2016-11-08', '1478608200Google-Is-Moving-Towards-A-More-Mobile-Focused-Index.png', 'Google Updated on Mobile Index', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Google explained that it sees more mobile searches than desktop searches on a daily basis. Google has started testing its mobile first index, which will basically take a gander at the mobile form of your site for its ranking signs and fall back on the desktop adaptation when there is no mobile version. The individuals who don&amp;#39;t have a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/web-development-services&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;mobile version of their site&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt; don&amp;#39;t have to stress. Google will simply utilize the desktop variant to rank the site. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://webmasters.googleblog.com/2016/11/mobile-first-indexing.html&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Google composed&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;, &amp;quot;On the off chance that you just have a desktop site, we&amp;#39;ll keep on indexing your desktop site fine and dandy, regardless of the possibility that we&amp;#39;re utilizing a mobile client agent to see your site.&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Here are a few proposals Google is offering website admins to get ready for the change:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;If you have a responsive site or a dynamic serving site where the essential contents and markup is identical crosswise over mobile and desktop, you shouldn&amp;#39;t need to change anything. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;If you have a site setup where the essential content and markup is diverse crosswise over mobile and desktop, you ought to think about rolling out some improvements to your site.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Make a point to serve organized markup for both the desktop and mobile versions. Destinations can check the proportionality of their organized markup crosswise over the desktop and mobile by writing the URLs of both variations into the Structured Data Testing Tool and contrasting the yield. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;At the point when adding organized information to a mobile website, avoid including a lot of markup that isn&amp;#39;t significant to the particular data content of every record. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Utilize the robots.txt testing tool to confirm that your mobile variant is open to Googlebot. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Websites don&amp;#39;t need to roll out improvements to their canonical links; we&amp;#39;ll keep on using these links as advisers to serve the proper results to a client seeking on desktop or mobile.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;In the event that you are a site owner who has just confirmed your desktop site in Search Console, please include and check your mobile variation. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', '2016-11-08 12:30:00'),
(84, '23', 'Know Your Currency Notes of Rs 500 And Rs 2000', '0', 'know-your-currency-notes-of-rs-500-and-rs-2000', 'The new Rs 500 and Rs 2000 currency notes are available at banks and ATMs. ', '2016-11-10', '1478775022Currency Notes of Rs.500 And Rs.2000.png', 'Notes of Rs 500 And Rs 2000', '', '', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The Government of India in an overcome move have demonetized Rs 500 and Rs 1000 currency notes with a specific end goal to battle corruption and black money issue in the nation. Meanwhile, new Rs 500 and Rs 2000 notes are already introduced. RBI has released the details of newly minted Rs 500 and Rs 2000 banknotes. The new Rs 500 note is completely different from the old note while the new Rs 2000 note has various major features to make it stand out. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Here are some must-know features of Rs.500 and Rs 2000 notes:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The Reserve Bank of India has come up with new Rs 500 and Rs 2000 denomination banknotes bearing a signature of Dr. Urjit R. Patel, Governor, Reserve Bank of India, and the year of printing &amp;#39;2016&amp;#39; and Swachh Bharat Logo printed on the reverse of the banknote. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The new notes will have Ashoka Pillar emblem on the right along with Mahatma Gandhi portrait and electrotype watermarks for visually impaired. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;Number panel with numerals growing from small to big on the top left side and bottom right side.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The note issued will be see-through register with denominational numeral 500 and 2000. IT is having a latent image with denominational numeral 500 and 2000 along with denominational numeral Rs 500 and Rs 2000 in Devnagari.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The new size of the Rs 500 denomination is 66mm x 150mm and the new color is stone grey,on the backside, there is an image of the Red Fort with Indian flag has been placed. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:transparent; font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;The new note of Rs 2000 has Motif of Mangalayan (Mars mission) on the reverse. The color of the note is magenta and the size is 66 mm &amp;times; 166 mm. Colour of the thread changes from green to blue when the note is tilted.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n', '2016-11-10 10:50:22'),
(85, '23', 'Content Keywords Feature Removed From Search Console', '0', 'content-keywords-feature-removed-from-search-console', 'Google has made another update with Search Console. Read to know more about it.', '2016-11-30', '1480518228Content _ Keywords _ Removed _ from _ Search _ Console.png', 'Content Keywords Feature Removed From Search Console', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Google loves to surprise everyone. Whether you are a regular user or a SEO professional, Google keeps coming up with shocking changes for everyone. In a recent update to Search Console, Google has removed the &amp;lsquo;content keywords&amp;rsquo; feature.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;lsquo;&lt;strong&gt;Content Keywords&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo; used to be an useful feature to check how Google bots see the keywords in the content. This was years ago when Search Console was still known as Google Webmaster Tool.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Since Google has introduced the feature of &amp;lsquo;&lt;strong&gt;Fetch and Render&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;, SEO professionals have found it more useful than &amp;lsquo;Content Keywords&amp;rsquo;. It&amp;rsquo;s visual representation of how Google bots see your page is more appealing to SEO professionals around the world than the traditional report pattern of &amp;lsquo;Content Keywords&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paritosh Sharma&lt;/strong&gt;, technical director of &lt;strong&gt;Rebelute Digital Solutions&lt;/strong&gt;, says &amp;ldquo;The keywords will always play an important role to create quality content for your website and we, as a &lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot;&gt;digital marketing agency&lt;/a&gt;, use lot of advance tools available, which are way efficient than Search Console&amp;rsquo;s &amp;lsquo;Content Keywords&amp;rsquo;, to take out list of highly relevant keywords for content creation for our clients.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Also, as Search Analytics section Search Console shows the list of keywords which has fetched traffic for your website, very less charm was left with the &amp;lsquo;&lt;strong&gt;Content Keywords&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;. Hence, Google took the step to eliminate &amp;lsquo;Content Keywords&amp;rsquo; from Search Console.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-11-30 15:03:48'),
(86, '24', 'Google Search Console Made Property Sets Richer With More Reporting Options', '0', 'google-search-console-made-property-sets-richer', 'Google Search Console property sets will now sport more reporting options.', '2016-12-12', '1481639127Google_search_Console-_Property-Sets.png', 'Google Search Console Made Property Sets Richer', 'Google Search Console ', 'Google Search Console ', '&lt;p&gt;Google seems to have vowed to get softer on SEO in 2017. After the recent joint announcement by Google and Bing on increasing the size limit of sitemap file to 50 MB, another move by Google is all set to make life of SEO professionals better in 2017. Google has announced that &lt;strong&gt;Google Search Console&lt;/strong&gt; will now have more varieties of reports for your property sets.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Earlier property sets used to allow combine different types of profiles into one report. But, basically you were able to see Search Analytics report you have combined for all the properties with property set.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Now, property sets option has become more flexible with more detailed reports of different data sets. You can get mobile usability report, review your AMP implementation, double-check rich cards or hreflang/internationalization markup and more. This will enable &lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot;&gt;SEO service providers&lt;/a&gt; to get more better insights of their client&amp;#39;s web site performance in both desktop and mobile SERPs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Not only this, Google has also confirmed that now you can add any verified property to a set.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Check the screen shot shared by Google.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Google Search Console&quot; src=&quot;http://rebelute.com/uploads/news/search%20console.png&quot; style=&quot;height:400px; width:544px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2016-12-13 14:25:27'),
(87, '25', '2013 Google Image Search UI Update Strikes Back, Affect More Countries', '0', '2013-google-image-search-ui-update-strikes-back', 'Google Image Search update from 2013 has been rolled out in more countries. Read to know more.', '2017-02-17', '1487343204Google Search Image Update.png', '2013 Image Search UI Update Strikes Back', 'Google image search, google image ui update', 'Google image search, google image ui update', '&lt;p&gt;A huge number of complaints have started flowing in from webmasters of countries like Germany, France and other countries regarding significant dip in the traffic from image searches.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Over three years ago Google had made changes to the design of their image search results and rolled out the update in US. The design change lead to drop of 60% in traffic from Google Image search back that time. A Google spokesperson recently confirmed about rolling out of UI change of Google Image search in other countries.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The UI roll out has affected huge number of websites and lot of webmasters has confirmed the drop in web traffic to their website. The &lt;a href=&quot;http://rebelute.com/digital-marketing&quot;&gt;digital marketing agencies&lt;/a&gt; are looking out for more ways to make the images on their client websites more compliant to updated guidelines. &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2017-02-17 14:53:24');
